entry.value: INSERT INTO encontros ( titulo, descricao, codigo, data, empresaid, turmaid, listaliberada, local, ativo, preworkid, posworkid, ferramenta, horas, encontrotipoid, liberarferramentaprework, avaliacaourl, realizado, avaliacaoresultado, salavirtual, mostrarforum, saladiasdisponivel, aulavirtual, feedback, apresentacao, arquivo_adicional, videoaulagravada, avaliacaoid, prebanca, prebancaliberada, instrutorid ) SELECT '${titulo}' AS titulo, '${descricao}' AS descricao, '' AS codigo, '${data}' AS data, '${empresaid}' AS empresaid, '${turmaid}' AS turmaid, '${listaliberada}' AS listaliberada, '${local}' AS local, '${ativo}' AS ativo, '${preworkid}' AS preworkid, '${posworkid}' AS posworkid, '${ferramenta}' AS ferramenta, '${horas}' AS horas, '${encontrotipoid}' AS encontrotipoid, '${liberarferramentaprework}' AS liberarferramentaprework, '${avaliacaourl}' AS avaliacaourl, '${realizado}' AS realizado, '${avaliacaoresultado}' AS avaliacaoresultado, '${salavirtual}' AS salavirtual, '${mostrarforum}' AS mostrarforum, '${saladiasdisponivel}' AS saladiasdisponivel, '${aulavirtual}' AS aulavirtual, ${feedback} AS feedback, '${apresentacao}' AS apresentacao, '${arquivo_adicional}' AS arquivo_adicional, '${videoaulagravada}' AS videoaulagravada, '${avaliacaoid}' AS avaliacaoid, '${prebanca}' AS prebanca, '${prebancaliberada}' AS prebancaliberada, '${instrutorid}' AS instrutorid FROM ( SELECT 1 as n ) DUMMY WHERE NOT EXISTS ( SELECT 1 FROM encontros newtable WHERE newtable.empresaid = '${empresaid}' AND newtable.turmaid = '${turmaid}' AND codigo = '${codigo}' )
